flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Load SQLite DB]
    B --> C[Reconstruct Patient SLL]
    B --> D[Reconstruct Doctor CLL]
    B --> E[Reconstruct Appointment Queue]
    C & D & E --> F[Streamlit UI Ready]
    F --> G{User Action}
    G -->|Add Patient| H[SLL.insert_at_end]
    H --> I[Save to SQLite]
    I --> F
    G -->|Add Visit| J[DLL.insert]
    J --> I
    G -->|Rotate Duty| K[CLL.rotate]
    K --> I
    G -->|Book Appointment| L[Queue.enqueue]
    L --> I
    G -->|Complete Appointment| M[Queue.dequeue]
    M --> I
    G -->|Back/Forward Visit| N[DLL.previous/next]
    N --> F
